about.home: http://multcomp.R-forge.R-project.org The publishers web page is http://www.crcpress.com/product/isbn/9781584885740
about.summary: Simultaneous tests and confidence intervals for general linear hypotheses in parametric models, including  linear, generalized linear, linear mixed effects, and survival models. The package includes demos reproducing analyzes presented in the book "Multiple Comparisons Using R" (Bretz, Hothorn,  Westfall, 2010, CRC Press).

name: r-multcomp
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.4-13" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-multcomp
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/multcomp_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/multcomp/multcomp_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d30f0357b8307e7feb574d6d307e0ebc6bdca66b2cc172980fa5309685885fdb

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-th.data >=1.0_2
    - r-codetools
    - r-mvtnorm >=1.0_10
    - r-sandwich >=2.3_0
    - r-survival >=2.39_4
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-th.data >=1.0_2
    - r-codetools
    - r-mvtnorm >=1.0_10
    - r-sandwich >=2.3_0
    - r-survival >=2.39_4

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('multcomp')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('multcomp')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://multcomp.R-forge.R-project.org The publishers web page is http://www.crcpress.com/product/isbn/9781584885740
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Simultaneous tests and confidence intervals for general linear hypotheses in parametric models, including  linear, generalized linear, linear mixed effects,
    and survival models. The package includes demos reproducing analyzes presented in the book "Multiple Comparisons Using R" (Bretz, Hothorn,  Westfall, 2010, CRC
    Press).
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
